I"5<p>SVN is still around, some things I have found useful</p>

<p>Add all files to SVN within current directory (recursively)</p>

<div class="language-bash highlighter-rouge"><div class="highlight"><pre class="highlight"><code>svn add <span class="nb">.</span> <span class="nt">--force</span>
</code></pre></div></div>
<p>Remove files from an add, within a folder (before commit)</p>
<div class="language-bash highlighter-rouge"><div class="highlight"><pre class="highlight"><code>svn revert <span class="nt">--recursive</span> folder_name
</code></pre></div></div>
